== 5...Nfd7 ==
Retreating the knight, preparing to trade bishops. White can choose to initiate the trade with '''[[/6. Bxe7/]]''', or they can go for the dangerous '''[[/6. h4/]]''', the '''Alekhine-Chatard attack'''.

